  <summary>1/6/2015--Introduced.
Hire More Heroes Act of 2015

This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code to add a provision to exempt any employee with coverage under a health care program administered by the Department of Defense, including the TRICARE program, or&#160;by&#160;the Veterans Administration, from classification as an eligible employee of an applicable large employer for purposes of the employer mandate&#160;under the Patient Protection and Affordable Care Act&#160;to provide such employees with minimum essential health care coverage.</summary>
</bill>
